🧑‍💼 Employee Directory - Frontend Project
A responsive, interactive, and vanilla JavaScript-powered Employee Directory web interface built using HTML, CSS, JavaScript, and Freemarker templates. This project was designed to demonstrate front-end development skills without backend dependencies.

🚀 Setup & Run Instructions
📁 Folder Structure
